# Badge Classes

Use these CSS helpers to display traffic-light status indicators:

- **`.badge-green`** – High confidence (≥90%)  
- **`.badge-yellow`** – Low sample or uncertain result  
- **`.badge-red`** – Pest found

## Example

```html
<span class="badge-green">✔ No pests</span>
<span class="badge-yellow">⚠ Low sample</span>
<span class="badge-red">✖ Pest found</span>
